<HEADLINE>  Young's Comeback Still in Progress </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	Stockton, Calif (AP) -- Bryant Young walks and runs easily now,  
and that's saying a lot considering the gruesome injury that ended 
his season last November. 
