<HEADLINE> Alabama Coach Admits to Affair </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	TUSCALOOSA, Ala. (AP) -- Alabama coach Mike DuBose on Thursday  
admitted to having an extramarital affair with a former secretary 
and apologized for misleading the public with earlier statements 
denying it. 
</P>
